#            <div class="gwblock_b "><div class="sense "><div class="sense-bullet">• </div><!-- End of DIV sense-bullet--><span class="sense_b after_bullet"><span class="SEP "> </span><span class="def parentof__def__is__sense_b">used when meeting or greeting someone</span></span><div class="sense_t after_bullet"><div class="examp "><span class="eg parentof__eg__is__examp">Hello, Paul. I haven't seen you for ages.</span></div><!-- End of DIV examp --><div class="examp "><span class="eg parentof__eg__is__examp">I know her vaguely - we've exchanged hellos a few times.</span></div><!-- End of DIV examp --><div class="examp "><span class="eg parentof__eg__is__examp">I just thought I'd call by and <strong class="b ">say</strong> hello.</span></div><!-- End of DIV examp --><div class="examp "><span class="eg parentof__eg__is__examp">And <strong class="b ">a big</strong> hello <span class="gl "><span class="SEP ">(= </span>welcome<span class="SEP ">)</span></span> to all the parents who've come to see the show.</span></div><!-- End of DIV examp --></div><!-- End of DIV sense_t after_bullet--></div><!-- End of DIV sense --><div class="sense "><div class="sense-bullet">• </div><!-- End of DIV sense-bullet--><span class="sense_b after_bullet"><span class="SEP "> </span><span class="def parentof__def__is__sense_b">something that is said at the beginning of a telephone conversation</span></span><div class="sense_t after_bullet"><div class="examp "><span class="eg parentof__eg__is__examp">"Hello, I'd like some information about your flights to the USA, please."</span></div><!-- End of DIV examp --></div><!-- End of DIV sense_t after_bullet--></div><!-- End of DIV sense --><div class="sense "><div class="sense-bullet">• </div><!-- End of DIV sense-bullet--><span class="sense_b after_bullet"><span class="SEP "> </span><span class="def parentof__def__is__sense_b">something that is said to attract someone's attention</span></span><div class="sense_t after_bullet"><div class="examp "><span class="eg parentof__eg__is__examp">The front door was open so she walked inside and called out, "Hello! Is there anybody in?"</span></div><!-- End of DIV examp --></div><!-- End of DIV sense_t after_bullet--></div><!-- End of DIV sense --><div class="sense "><div class="sense-bullet">• </div><!-- End of DIV sense-bullet--><span class="sense_b after_bullet"><span class="SEP "> </span><span class="lab parentof__lab__is__sense_b"><span class="usage " title="Used in relaxed situations, for example with friends and family. Used more in speech.">informal </span> </span> <span class="SEP "> </span><span class="def parentof__def__is__sense_b">said to someone who has just said or done something stupid, especially something that shows they are not noticing what is happening around them</span></span><div class="sense_t after_bullet"><div class="examp "><span class="eg parentof__eg__is__examp">She asked me if I'd just arrived and I was like 'hello, I've been here for an hour.'</span></div><!-- End of DIV examp --></div><!-- End of DIV sense_t after_bullet--></div><!-- End of DIV sense --><div class="sense "><div class="sense-bullet">• </div><!-- End of DIV sense-bullet--><span class="sense_b after_bullet"><span class="SEP "> </span><span class="lab parentof__lab__is__sense_b"><span class="usage " title="Words or phrases that sound old-fashioned, not modern.">old-fashioned </span> </span> <span class="SEP "> </span><span class="def parentof__def__is__sense_b">an expression of surprise</span></span><div class="sense_t after_bullet"><div class="examp "><span class="eg parentof__eg__is__examp">Hello, this is very strange - I know that man.</span></div><!-- End of DIV examp --></div><!-- End of DIV sense_t after_bullet--></div><!-- End of DIV sense --></div><!-- End of DIV gwblock_b --></div><!-- End of DIV gwblock --></div><!-- End of DIV posblock_b --></div><!-- End of DIV posblock --></p>
